      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Up for sale is a vehicle in fair condition that serves as a reliable daily driver but shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor door dings, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. While it runs and drives well, there are some minor mechanical issues that will need attention eventually, such as a slow oil leak and aging suspension components. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone needing dependable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and a few upcoming weekend projects.",
