      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! It honestly breaks my heart a little to see this beauty go, but it's time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as pampered. I\u2019ve truly babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and treated like a member of the family. She looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor! You might find a tiny, microscopic mark if you really go looking with a magnifying glass, but honestly, she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with a capital L, you\u2019ve found it. Come on by, have a coffee, and let's get you behind the wheel of your dream car!",
      "price": 48500.0,
