      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously sorted example featuring a bespoke Stage 1 ECU remap optimized for linear power delivery and peak thermal efficiency. This specimen boasts a reinforced dual-clutch transmission with recalibrated shift logic and a zero-lash drivetrain. The chassis has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and high-durometer bushing upgrade, ensuring surgical precision and torsional rigidity. Maintenance has been obsessive, with fluid cycles performed at half-intervals using high-zinc synthetics to preserve internal tolerances. The exterior features a multi-stage paint correction sealed under a 9H ceramic matrix. This is a turnkey, concours-grade machine for the discerning pilot who demands zero mechanical compromise.",
